author: Muriel Draaisma,Laura Howells
title: Toronto has total of 3,546 COVID-19 cases
description: Toronto has a total of 3,546 cases of COVID-19 as the pandemic continues, the city reported on Sunday afternoon.
content:
Toronto has a total of 3,546 cases of COVID-19 as the pandemic continues, the city reported on Sunday afternoon.
In a news release, the city said the total includes 3,212 confirmed cases and 334 probable ones.
